      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>diced chicken breast</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>baharat</strong>, <strong>cayenne pepper </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>soy sauce</strong> and give everything a good mix up until the chicken is coated</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick)<strong> </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated chicken</strong> and cook for 4-5 min until starting to brown</p>",
