      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Drain and rinse the <strong>chickpeas</strong></p><p>Combine the<strong> pomegranate molasses</strong>, <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> in a large bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>pomegranate dressing</strong></p>",
