      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>couscous</strong> to a large heatproof bowl with the<strong> chopped dates</strong>, 130ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[260ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong>, cover with a tea towel and set aside</p><p>Fluff with a fork before serving</p>",
