    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the butternut squash is fork-tender, add it to the pan with the <strong>drained chickpeas</strong> and cook for 4-5 min further or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>Moroccan-style</strong> <strong>chicken & butternut squash</strong></p>",
