    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>rocket </strong>and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped parsley</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) to the bowl with the couscous</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> of the<strong> pomegranate dressing </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) and gently mix it all together – this is your<strong> couscous salad</strong></p>",
