      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>couscous salad</strong> with the<strong> Moroccan-style chicken & butternut squash</strong> to the side</p><p>Top with the <strong>remaining chopped parsley </strong>and drizzle over the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>pomegranate dressing</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
